Class J4210U.TagInfo

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    J4210U

    public static class J4210U.TagInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    TagInfo class contains information about the tag. For example its EPC length, TID length, type of chip, Chip name, User memory size, etc.
